<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3150793" xml-lang="en-US" level="1" l10n="U" oldref="1"><link href="text/schart/01/05020101.xhp" name="Alignment">Alignment</link></paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3125864" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="2">Modifies the alignment of the title.</paragraph>
</section>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3145748" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="4">Some of the options are not available for all types of labels. For example, there are different options for 2D and 3D object labels.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3151114" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="E" localize="false"><link href="text/schart/00/00000004.xhp#frttya"><embedvar href="text/schart/00/00000004.xhp#wie"/></link></paragraph>
<embed href="text/schart/01/05020201.xhp#schreibr"/>
<paragraph role="note" id="par_id3150717" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="3">Please note that problems may arise in displaying labels if the size of your chart is too small. You can avoid this by either enlarging the view or decreasing the font size.</paragraph>
